ts into it."},{"content":"Add cooled vegetables from Varoma and simmering basket to salad bowl and set aside."},{"content":"Place dill, oil, vinegar and salt into mixing bowl and mix <b>30 sec\/speed 6<b>. Transfer into salad bowl, stir to coat all vegetables with dressing, adjust seasoning to taste and serve garnished with extra chopped fresh dill."}],"hintsAndTricks":["For a creamy pink version of the salad, instead of making the vinaigrette in <b>step 7,<b> dress the cooled vegetables with sour cream or mayonnaise (quantity to taste), stir gently to combine, season to taste and garnish with chopped dill.","In <b>step 5,<b> if you are in a hurry to cool the vegetables, run cold water over each vegetable separately while they are still in the Varoma dish, Varoma tray and simmering basket.<br>- For a traditional Russian flavour, omit the vinegar."],"basicInfo":["easy","20m","1h 10m","8 portions"]}